<article class="rounded-lg lg:w-1/2 m-1 p-6">
  <h1
    class="hidden lg:block text-5xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-10 text-center"
  >
    ¡Solicita tu presupuesto!
  </h1>
  <h1
    class="block lg:hidden text-3xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3 text-center"
  >
    Consulta
  </h1>
  <p
    class="text-gray-600 mb-6 text-justify m-auto lg:text-xl lg:w-2/3 text-base w-11/12 md:w-9/12"
  >
    Será un placer atender cualquier consulta que tengas. No dudes en
    contactarnos para recibir una cotización personalizada para tu próximo
    proyecto digital.
  </p>

  <form
    class="bg-white rounded-lg lg:p-8 sm:w-3/4 lg:w-3/4 mx-auto flex flex-col gap-6 text-gray-800"
  >
    <label class="flex flex-col">
      <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-1">Email</span>
      <input
        type="email"
        class="border border-gray-300 rounded-lg p-3 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 bg-gray-200"
        placeholder="name@example.com"
        required
      />
    </label>

    <label class="flex flex-col">
      <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-1">Nombre</span>
      <input
        type="text"
        class="border border-gray-300 rounded-lg p-3 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 bg-gray-200"
        placeholder="Jony"
        required
      />
    </label>

    <label class="flex flex-col">
      <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-1">Teléfono</span>
      <input
        type="tel"
        class="border border-gray-300 rounded-lg p-3 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 bg-gray-200"
        placeholder="Ej: 11-23656767"
        required
      />
    </label>

    <label class="flex flex-col">
      <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-1"
        >Nombre de la empresa</span
      >
      <input
        type="text"
        class="border border-gray-300 rounded-lg p-3 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 bg-gray-200"
        required
      />
    </label>

    <label class="flex flex-col">
      <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-1"
        >A qué se dedica su empresa*</span
      >
      <textarea
        id="business-description"
        class="border resize-none border-gray-300 rounded-lg p-3 h-32 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 bg-gray-200"
        placeholder="Mi empressa se dedica a ..."
        required></textarea>
    </label>

    <label class="flex flex-col">
      <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-1"
        >Plataforma WEB: URL actual (si posee)</span
      >
      <input
        type="url"
        class="border border-gray-300 rounded-lg p-3 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 bg-gray-200"
        placeholder="www.sitioweb.com"
        required
      />
    </label>

    <label class="flex flex-col">
      <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-1"
        >Describe sus necesidades*</span
      >
      <textarea
        id="needs-description"
        class="border resize-none border-gray-300 rounded-lg p-3 h-32 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 bg-gray-200"
        placeholder="Mi empresa esta necesitando..."
        required></textarea>
    </label>

    <div class="text-start">
      <button
        type="submit"
        class="bg-customColor text-white py-3 px-10 rounded-lg shadow transition duration-300 ease-in-out"
      >
        Enviar
      </button>
    </div>
  </form>
</article>

